mittens. I'm found in the paws of playful kittens. What am I? \n"))
                if q1_l2 == 'Yarn' or q1_l2 == 'yarn':
                    print('You got it!')
                    q2_l2 = str(input("2. Tool of thief, toy of queen. 
Always used to be unseen. Sign of joy, sign of sorrow. Giving all likeness 
